metadata.name: The Space Between Us
metadata.description:
An immediate sense of comfort distracts from the reality within. 
This photograph displays two individuals, clearly together, as they are alone in their surroundings, but feel so distant and apart. Meanwhile, the water bottle placed between them tells the whole story. While the pair sits before this vast body of water, displaying its purity and openness, the intensity between them remains contained, separating them.
